OL,3,CRicky Tomlinson & Sue Johnston reunite
OL,4,Cfor new travel show
OL,6,FRicky Tomlinson has returned to
OL,7,Ftelevision screens in a brand new show
OL,8,Falongside long-time co-star Sue
OL,9,FJohnston.
OL,11,FTo celebrate four decades on screen
OL,12,Ftogether, they're starring in a new
OL,13,FMore4 series, visiting landmark places
OL,14,Ffrom their lives and the special
OL,15,Fdestinations the pair have always
OL,16,Fwanted to see together.
