OL,6,FReflecting on his time on the long-
OL,7,Frunning BBC comedy, Ricky said: "Jim
OL,8,FRoyle was exactly the same (as me). I
OL,9,Fliked his character. I like telly!"
OL,11,FThe three-part series Ricky, Sue & a
OL,12,FTrip or Two, will air for the first
OL,13,Ftime on Tuesday night at 9pm.
