OL,3,CRicky Tomlinson & Sue Johnston reunite
OL,4,Cfor new travel show
OL,6,F"Channel 4 will have a job to do
OL,7,Fkeeping us both on our best behaviour
OL,8,Falong with the friends we meet along
OL,9,Fthe way."
OL,11,FBoth actors have remained in the North
OL,12,FWest all of their lives.
OL,14,F"I don't want to live anywhere else,
OL,15,FSue doesn't want to live anywhere
OL,16,Felse. I love where I am, I love the
OL,17,Flocal people where I am. I've had
OL,18,Fgreat neighbours."
